  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.label>形体不稳定</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.label>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.description>带有这种基因的异型在性高潮时变得更加不稳定——一旦达到临界水平，分裂进程将会启动。</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.description>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.0.label>稳定</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.0.label>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.1.label>激动</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.1.label>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.2.label>不稳定</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.2.label>
  <rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.3.label>临界</rjw_genes_orgasmic_mytosis_hediff.stages.3.label>

  <rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.label>分裂震撼</rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.label>
  <rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.description>最近刚进行过一次成功的分裂。 由于这是一次耗费精力的过程，需要一定时间的修养。 此时无法产生新的胚芽。</rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.description>
  <rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.stages.0.label>逐渐恢复</rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.stages.0.label>
  <rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.stages.1.label>焕然一新</rjw_genes_mytosis_shock_hediff.stages.1.label>


